 STEP 2: Install Java (Required for Jenkins)
Jenkins requires Java.
Check if Java is installed:
java -version
If not installed, install OpenJDK 17:
sudo dnf install java-17-openjdk -y
Verify again:
java -version
âœ…
You should see Java 17 version details.
